{"type": "article", "id": 26597, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-10T06:51:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27397, "name": "VivaBoo"}, {"id": 27398, "name": "Spiral lamp"}, {"id": 27399, "name": "Candy collection glassware"}, {"id": 27400, "name": "Mushroom Lamp"}, {"id": 27401, "name": "Trace clock"}, {"id": 27402, "name": "Piquentum St Vital"}, {"id": 27403, "name": "Gongdreen"}, {"id": 27404, "name": "Campana brothers"}, {"id": 27405, "name": "ZISION X IDMIX"}, {"id": 27406, "name": "Studio Ayaskan"}, {"id": 27407, "name": "Studio Sonda"}, {"id": 27408, "name": "Andrii Kovalskyi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151943WGxC8B4FozIHSTbK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>VivaBoo by Gongdreen</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://gongdreen.com/\">Gongdreen</a> 的设计师们之前就制作过一系列模仿了动物造型的产品，这一次他们参照了或许是这个星球上最奇怪的动物，鸭嘴兽。这款名为 VivaBoo 的茶滤有着非常可爱的外形，使用起来也非常方便：打开它白色的“肚子”，装入茶叶后把它挂在杯沿上就行了。茶滤一共有三种颜色可选，<a href=\"http://gongdreen.com/?product=vivaboo-tea-infuser\">售价为 12 美元</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181721YvFVi3O84Z1Ln9eo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63970588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181722dpmTLa3VWe0qu9hz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181722kgMjCVwWcYIyADHF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817220IkRyn9So3HlMtgb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52205882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181723L12bReMBZuNYqo5K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.30633284\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817235mKdODWp9zLj4X16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Spiral lamp by Andrii Kovalskyi</h2>\n<p class=\"\">光是直线传播的，不过 Andrii Kovalskyi 设计的这一系列名为 Spiral 的螺旋状的吊灯和壁灯则提供了一个新的启发。高科技的 LED 灯带有着很高的灵活度，同薄木条结合后像是有一双无形的手在空中挥舞着光的束带。虽然整体造型有点过于华丽了，但这样的灯具的确能为房间增色不少。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181724SNpR7Q3HlvDOgZTs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817258utoeqIG1SHOl9Es.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817255XlGCMFTAsr2o0q4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181725fzNaKCEBObUJ7Pg0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181726I0BivLKDTsgl4PtE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Candy collection glassware by Campana brothers</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://campanas.com.br/en\">Campana 兄弟</a>去年曾为 LASVIT 设计过一款色彩斑澜的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/campana-brothers-lasvit-06-24-2015/\">枝形吊灯</a>，这一次他们将类似的概念用在了这一套同样名为 Candy 的玻璃器皿上。手吹玻璃中的色带看上去像是把焦糖放在器皿的顶端，沿着轮廓滑下所造成的痕迹。Campana 兄弟在挑选颜色时只是将浅色系和深色系搭配在一起，并不遵守其他特定的原则，每一个器皿也因此独一无二。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181726bSFcf7wmWr1PJCGX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181727is1N4XHVrdct6AjF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181728QJIPqz1uWmeDSOyr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181728Odg8U1G7HVhoZDIt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3202934\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181729rRW5z93CuLtc7Epy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03422983\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181729LCjZaTMiI6AEbyWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09046455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Mushroom Lamp by ZISION X IDMIX</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这款既是台灯又是手机充电座的 Mushroom Lamp 由 ZISION 工作室和 IDMIX 共同推出。它内置五千毫安时的锂聚合物电池，作为台灯使用时可以持续照明八小时，如果同时为手机充电的的话也能提供五个小时的照明，兼顾了美观的造型以及实用性。这款产品目前正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/529636401/a-mushroom-lamp-can-charge-your-iphone\">Kickstarter</a> 上进行众筹，价格为 69 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181730NW4Y67cIneMlLFr2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181730PNw3CpgRT4nqf8KS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181731IK9iDgAQ1qh7ueFw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63970588\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817329Zh1pSoGH4amT6dI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817341AmEBr4a08CUVZgj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181734OxCdtmfGQs8Neay2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Trace clock by Studio Ayaskan</h2>\n<p class=\"\">还记得我们去年介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/16967.html\">一款沙子钟</a>吗？这一次，<a href=\"http://ayaskan.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Studio Ayaskan</a> 将介质转变为了液体，以激光在水中射出的痕迹作为指针，紫色的线条须臾间就在水中消散。相比以小时显示时刻的沙子钟，这款 Trace clock 看上去多了一份不确定性，也更好地表现出时间的飞速流逝。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181735cPQ50VUqJrYFfRiE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181735O8gQmMGHa5JCZbXs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181736WiY0lOKCqLG73k2o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181736iMTIhWpaHV4zomne.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181736nsRXFKvg9xHaL2O5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181737wTufKlrWQqgXkRGH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Piquentum St Vital by Studio Sonda</h2>\n<p class=\"\">葡萄酒的酿造年份往往都会直接在包装上注明，但是不少人并不能真正理解葡萄在那一年收获究竟意味着什么。为了解决这个问题，Studio Sonda 同气象部门合作，为 Piquentum St Vital 设计的新包装暗藏了玄机：标签上分布着 12 个大小不一、被水打湿的圆圈，表现的是当年每个月的降雨量。这个讨巧的设计很直观地体现出了大自然的多样性，向更多人普及了酿造知识。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181737YA2SmXxdwsuipv8h.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63447433\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181738e2MobL7wqDripvyI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4792176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181738r2AFtIm9Qd0gL1Eb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817393fIwZ9sG07k26re5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56356968\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181739vrVKnJfBeIL8i26P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}